<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 06:09:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>黎巴嫩哈马斯官员被杀是否会导致与真主党的关系进一步升级？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/will-the-killing-of-hamas-leader-in-lebanon-lead-to-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-cc0f-dc35-adee-cc4f27010000</link><description>自战争开始以来，真主党一直小心翼翼地将其对以色列的日常袭击限制在边境附近的一小片土地上，以保持在战争水平以下。 问题是真主党将如何应对在其主场发生的暗杀事件</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 04:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/will-the-killing-of-hamas-leader-in-lebanon-lead-to-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-cc0f-dc35-adee-cc4f27010000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯高级官员阿鲁里在贝鲁特被杀后人质谈判停止，真主党威胁以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-live/hezbollah-threatens-israel-after-top-hamas-official-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut/0000018c-ccf4-d266-a9bf-edf645660000</link><description>法国联合国特使表示，联合国安理会可能于周三在红海举行会议 ■ 哈马斯高级官员萨拉赫·阿鲁里 (Salah al-Arouri) 与哈马斯两名高级军事领导人一起在贝鲁特被杀 ■ 真主党称杀戮“不会得不到回应”，并向以色列边境发射导弹镇 ■ 以色列士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 21,978 人死亡，57,697 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 03:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-live/hezbollah-threatens-israel-after-top-hamas-official-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut/0000018c-ccf4-d266-a9bf-edf645660000</guid></item><item><title>实际上，为什么不将定居者转移出以色列呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/actually-why-not-transfer-settlers-out-of-israel/0000018c-cbc4-dc35-adee-cbc6884a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 01:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/actually-why-not-transfer-settlers-out-of-israel/0000018c-cbc4-dc35-adee-cbc6884a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须停止殴打和羞辱巴勒斯坦囚犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-opinion/israel-must-stop-the-beating-and-humiliation-of-palestinian-prisoners/0000018c-cbf7-dc35-adee-cbf7961c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 00:56:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-opinion/israel-must-stop-the-beating-and-humiliation-of-palestinian-prisoners/0000018c-cbf7-dc35-adee-cbf7961c0000</guid></item><item><title>阿巴斯希望美国给予他在加沙的地位并让以色列加入。但可以吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/abbas-expects-the-u-s-to-give-him-authority-in-gaza-but-can-it/0000018c-cbbf-ddba-abad-cbbf79fe0000</link><description>虽然以色列避免讨论战后第二天，但埃及已准备好与巴勒斯坦权力机构合作，并希望能够帮助防止加沙人大规模移民</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:24:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/abbas-expects-the-u-s-to-give-him-authority-in-gaza-but-can-it/0000018c-cbbf-ddba-abad-cbbf79fe0000</guid></item><item><title>美国呼吁极右翼以色列部长主张将巴勒斯坦人撤出加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-calls-out-israeli-ministers-for-advocating-transfer-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cbec-d4e1-ad8f-fffd3ad60000</link><description>这份声明是美国罕见地不及时批评以色列，更罕见的是它明确点名点名斯莫特里奇和本-格维尔</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-calls-out-israeli-ministers-for-advocating-transfer-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cbec-d4e1-ad8f-fffd3ad60000</guid></item><item><title>与辛瓦尔协调，与真主党联系在一起：谁是哈马斯最高领导人萨利赫·阿鲁里？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/coordinated-with-sinwar-tied-to-hezbollah-who-was-hamas-official-saleh-al-arouri/0000018c-cbb3-d4e1-ad8f-ffb31c580000</link><description>周二晚上，阿鲁里在贝鲁特南部被杀，他是哈马斯政治派别中一位有影响力和魅力的领导人。他是多起针对以色列的恐怖袭击的幕后黑手，并参与了人质交换谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/coordinated-with-sinwar-tied-to-hezbollah-who-was-hamas-official-saleh-al-arouri/0000018c-cbb3-d4e1-ad8f-ffb31c580000</guid></item><item><title>一定是艾伦·德肖维茨为以色列辩护，反对种族灭绝指控吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-02/ty-article/.highlight/alan-dershowitz-cant-be-israels-only-option-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-cae3-d4e1-ad8f-fef3a20e0000</link><description>为什么以色列必须求助于德肖维茨——多年来他已被证明是从事“德肖维茨生意”的——而不是一个真正具有国际法诚意的人？</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 18:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-02/ty-article/.highlight/alan-dershowitz-cant-be-israels-only-option-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-cae3-d4e1-ad8f-fef3a20e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名周二在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-north-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018c-cb16-d4e1-ad8f-ffb776490000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，在导致参谋军士死亡的事件中，另有三人受重伤。苏菲安·达加什 (Sufian Dagash)，曾在工程兵部队服役</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 17:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-north-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018c-cb16-d4e1-ad8f-ffb776490000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯确认最高领导人萨拉赫·阿鲁里在贝鲁特爆炸中丧生；指责以色列暗杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/hamas-confirms-top-leader-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut-blames-israel-for-assassination/0000018c-cb0a-d4e1-ad8f-ffbb95e30000</link><description>阿鲁里是哈马斯政治局副局长，仅次于伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚。黎巴嫩报道称爆炸是由以色列无人机袭击造成的</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 17:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/hamas-confirms-top-leader-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut-blames-israel-for-assassination/0000018c-cb0a-d4e1-ad8f-ffbb95e30000</guid></item><item><title>那个被称为傀儡但自比为希律王的人又回到了以色列外交部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/king-herod-or-netanyahus-puppet-yisrael-katz-is-back-in-israels-foreign-ministry/0000018c-c5f5-d6c4-ab8d-e5f58e010000</link><description>外交部长伊斯雷尔·卡茨与伊莱·科恩交换职位，回到了被剥夺了大部分权力和声望的工作岗位，但他着眼于更大的奖品：当本杰明·内塔尼亚胡退出政治舞台时</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 16:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/king-herod-or-netanyahus-puppet-yisrael-katz-is-back-in-israels-foreign-ministry/0000018c-c5f5-d6c4-ab8d-e5f58e010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将任命法官并为国际法院加沙种族灭绝听证会准备辩护团队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-appoint-judge-prepare-defense-team-for-icj-hearing-on-gaza-genocide/0000018c-ca94-ddba-abad-cab56ecf0000</link><description>以色列正在组建一个部际小组，准备对南非提交的请愿书进行辩护。以色列人权专家指责以色列执法人员没有对以色列政客呼吁种族清洗和种族灭绝的极端言论采取行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 16:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-appoint-judge-prepare-defense-team-for-icj-hearing-on-gaza-genocide/0000018c-ca94-ddba-abad-cab56ecf0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查发现，75％的犹太以色列人拒绝美国将加沙战争转移到新阶段的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/75-of-jewish-israelis-reject-u-s-demand-to-shift-gaza-war-to-new-phase-poll-finds/0000018c-caa4-d4e1-ad8f-feb5bdda0000</link><description>56%的阿拉伯受访者表示以色列应该屈服于美国的压力，大多数左翼犹太人也同意战争应该转向精确瞄准哈马斯领导人</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 15:19:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/75-of-jewish-israelis-reject-u-s-demand-to-shift-gaza-war-to-new-phase-poll-finds/0000018c-caa4-d4e1-ad8f-feb5bdda0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼议员威胁：“我们将与哈马斯、真主党打交道，然后是最高法院”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/far-right-lawmaker-threatens-we-will-deal-with-hamas-hezbollah-then-the-supreme-court/0000018c-caa6-d4e1-ad8f-feb71d610000</link><description>高等法院周一否决了一项重要的司法政变法后，来自 Ben-Gvir 领导的 Otzma Yehudit 党的 MK Tzvika Foghel 在 X 上发布了这一威胁。战时内阁成员甘茨称这种比较“卑鄙可耻”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 15:16:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/far-right-lawmaker-threatens-we-will-deal-with-hamas-hezbollah-then-the-supreme-court/0000018c-caa6-d4e1-ad8f-feb71d610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军慈善机构提拔支持“扁平化”加沙的分析师，称自由主义者是“犹太国家的敌人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-charity-promotes-analyst-who-supports-flattening-gaza-loathes-liberal-values/0000018c-ca11-ddba-abad-cab17ea40000</link><description>以色列国防军之友邀请颇具争议的评论员埃利亚胡·约西安 (Eliyahu Yossian) 在一群受益者面前发表讲话。他此前曾声称，以色列应该在对 10 月 7 日大屠杀的立即反应中杀害 50,000 名加沙人</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:53:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-charity-promotes-analyst-who-supports-flattening-gaza-loathes-liberal-values/0000018c-ca11-ddba-abad-cab17ea40000</guid></item><item><title>3000万年前埃及的早期猴子吃什么？现在我们知道了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-02/ty-article/what-did-early-monkeys-eat-in-egypt-30-million-years-ago-now-we-know/0000018c-ca62-ddba-abad-cae32e5c0000</link><description>根据对 3400 万至 2900 万年前猴子化石牙齿的分析，缺乏广泛的牙釉质碎裂表明它们都吃软食。换句话说，水果</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-02/ty-article/what-did-early-monkeys-eat-in-egypt-30-million-years-ago-now-we-know/0000018c-ca62-ddba-abad-cae32e5c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须立即撤出加沙。现在是人质，后来是辛瓦尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-get-out-of-gaza-immediately-hostages-now-sinwar-later/0000018c-ca03-d4e1-ad8f-feb384af0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-get-out-of-gaza-immediately-hostages-now-sinwar-later/0000018c-ca03-d4e1-ad8f-feb384af0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其拘留了 33 名涉嫌为以色列从事间谍活动的人，并正在寻找另外 13 名据信与摩萨德有联系的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/turkey-detains-33-people-suspected-of-spying-for-israel/0000018c-ca73-d4e1-ad8f-fef3c4380000</link><description>嫌疑人因涉嫌计划代表以色列情报机构开展包括“追捕、袭击和绑架”居住在土耳其的外国人在内的活动而被拘留。辛贝特领导人表示，他们将在“每个地方”追捕哈马斯领导人，包括土耳其</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 13:53:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/turkey-detains-33-people-suspected-of-spying-for-israel/0000018c-ca73-d4e1-ad8f-fef3c4380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院法官以决定性多数宣布内塔尼亚胡的司法政变宣告结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/decisive-majority-of-israels-high-court-justices-declares-netanyahus-judicial-coup-dead/0000018c-c9c4-ddba-abad-cbe59ebf0000</link><description>反对微弱选票的警告最终证明是虚假的操纵，因为这会在战争时期分裂人民。内塔尼亚胡对下一个决定更感兴趣：禁止司法部长宣布他不适合担任公职的法律</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 12:30:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/decisive-majority-of-israels-high-court-justices-declares-netanyahus-judicial-coup-dead/0000018c-c9c4-ddba-abad-cbe59ebf0000</guid></item><item><title>新星狂欢节幸存者起诉以色列安全机构，要求赔偿 2 亿谢克尔，理由是其未能阻止哈马斯的屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/nova-survivors-sue-israeli-security-agencies-for-200m-over-hamas-massacre/0000018c-c969-d4e1-ad8f-fdf974c20000</link><description>“即使人们担心恐怖分子渗透到该地区，他们也没有驱散狂欢……这令人难以理解” ■ 哈马斯大屠杀幸存者提起的史无前例的诉讼认为，以色列国防军、辛贝特和以色列警察疏忽大意</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 12:22:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/nova-survivors-sue-israeli-security-agencies-for-200m-over-hamas-massacre/0000018c-c969-d4e1-ad8f-fdf974c20000</guid></item></channel></rss>